Setup

Install the latest near-cli-rs libraries

`cargo install near-cli-rs`

Note: You may need to update rust with `rustup update`

Once near client is installed `cp config.js.example` to `config.js` and update the config file to insert the admin signing address. 


Usage

node submitTx.js <action> <target>

Available actions

freeze/unfreeze/destroy : <target> is the address to affect

mint : <target> is the full raw amount to mint to tether-treasury.near. i.e. 100 USDt = 100000000

confirm/unconfirm : <target> is the msig id to confirm/unconfirm

